a few steps from the monastery."},{"@language":"fr","@value":"Le monastère des Augustins est facilement accessible avec les lignes de tramway 1 (direction Europaplatz) et 5 (direction Zoopark). L'arrêt \"Augustinerkloster/ Lutherstätte\" se trouve à seulement quelques pas du monastère."},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b61","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"de","@value":"Das Augustinerkloster erreichen Sie bequem mit der Stadtbahnlinie 1 (Richtung Europaplatz) und 5 (Richtung Zoopark). Die Haltestelle \"Augustinerkloster/ Lutherstätte befindet sich nur wenige Schritte vom Kloster entfernt."}},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b62","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"en","@value":"You can easily reach the Augustinian Monastery by tram lines 1 (direction Europaplatz) and 5 (direction Zoopark). The \"Augustinerkloster/Lutherstätte\" stop is just a few steps from the monastery."}},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b63","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"fr","@value":"Le monastère des Augustins est facilement accessible avec les lignes de tramway 1 (direction Europaplatz) et 5 (direction Zoopark). L'arrêt \"Augustinerkloster/ Lutherstätte\" se trouve à seulement quelques pas du monastère."}}],"thuecat:gettingThere":[{"@language":"de","@value":"Vom Stadtring (Staufenbergallee) kommend auf den inneren Stadtring (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), dann über Boyneburgufer in die Straße \"Am Hügel\". Am Ende nach links abbiegen."},{"@language":"en","@value":"Coming from the city ring road (Staufenbergallee) onto the inner city ring (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), then via Boyneburgufer into the street \"Am Hügel.\" At the end, turn left."},{"@language":"fr","@value":"Depuis le boulevard périphérique (Staufenbergallee), prenez le boulevard périphérique intérieur (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), puis passez par le quai Boyneburg vers la rue \"Am Hügel\". À la fin, tournez à gauche."},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b55","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"de","@value":"Vom Stadtring (Staufenbergallee) kommend auf den inneren Stadtring (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), dann über Boyneburgufer in die Straße \"Am Hügel\". Am Ende nach links abbiegen."}},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b56","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"en","@value":"Coming from the city ring road (Staufenbergallee) onto the inner city ring (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), then via Boyneburgufer into the street \"Am Hügel.\" At the end, turn left."}},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b57","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language":"fr","@value":"Depuis le boulevard périphérique (Staufenbergallee), prenez le boulevard périphérique intérieur (Juri-Gagarin-Ring), puis passez par le quai Boyneburg vers la rue \"Am Hügel\". À la fin, tournez à gauche."}}],"thuecat:parking":[{"@language":"de","@value":"Bitte nutzen Sie das Parkleitsystem der Stadt Erfurt. Weitere Parkplätze sind am Juri-Gagarin-Ring verfügbar (kostenpflichtig)."},{"@language":"en","@value":"Please use the city of Erfurt's parking guidance system. Additional parking spaces are available at Juri-Gagarin-Ring (paid)."},{"@language":"fr","@value":"Veuillez utiliser le système de guidage de stationnement de la ville d'Erfurt. Des places de parking supplémentaires sont disponibles sur le Juri-Gagarin-Ring (payant)."},{"@id":"genid-66bd5bdb641047d8ad0a83edd26b83f540663548-b58","@type":["schema:Thing","schema:Intangible","schema:ComputerLanguage","thuecat:Html"],"schema:value":{"@language"